Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.41,0:01:30.91,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)}时间对我太迅速
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.01,0:01:36.61,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)}一无所知地空虚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.01,0:01:40.01,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)}聚集的语言
